{"tid":1771142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔區朋友！唔該入黎幫幫手！","createTime":"2019-12-05T15:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T03:31:01.000Z","uid":193812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aca0713c2d07d7939a557617c748054d4fdd56df","tid":1771142,"uid":193812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OPiuf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OPiuf3.jpg&h=a6426082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借位一用，幫朋友post！<br />\n<br />\n朋友的狗昨晚(4號)9時左右受驚下，在大埔頭走失，請問各位可否幫眼留意：<br />\n-唐狗女<br />\n-黃黃地色<br />\n-叫花生<br />\n-頸有金屬鍊（其他狗帶包括Gps在受驚時鬆脫）<br />\n-有途人曾在太平工業村見過<br />\n-好細膽<br />\n<br />\n請大家見到佢時，不要叫佢追佢，因為佢好怕人，會即刻走。請離遠靜靜吊住佢尾，有消息請通知，感謝各位<br />\n<br />\n[05.12.19 - 2200update]  <br />\n<br />\n2100後有街坊喺帝欣苑與梅樹坑一帶見到，疑似走落河道，多草嗰part，去向不明<br />\n<br />\n目前見過佢嘅地方包括：大埔頭勤園、大埔頭北公廁、嘉敬里、水圍近渠務署設施、帝欣苑林村河<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花生已經唔見左超過24小時，主人們都好擔心。<br />\n希望各位大埔巴絲可以幫幫手留意下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c79dc8be5bdd6f271fb46e2caa6433433636595","tid":1771142,"uid":193812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14759762b1ae4403f311eb49f2e16d711a2c9daf","tid":1771142,"uid":23281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c2063e39e3fd7581b10d1f7bdaecf5ba859520c","tid":1771142,"uid":213529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ffb5c52c39d69a47d786240876c64bd0b775ae","tid":1771142,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已經被入侵!!!星期六行動post冇人推，大家入黎同我推爆佢春袋!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hksuckagain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhksuckagain&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=b1e09427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hksuckagain</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【緊急!!!連登冇人推行動post!!!】和理非12.7一齊遊車河塞春袋!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ed61f5d18561bb3edf16ed4947ffc7d72fdc02a","tid":1771142,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"幫手推 希望快啲搵返"},{"pid":"cb31bcf39e8b6f6dd8ae17c9f4cfe9b4244338d0","tid":1771142,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9357d57d011ce05d367ae83b8676fc5c57ad9086","tid":1771142,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bc3544af4b85f3468be326cd2cd3e8883aa8e0","tid":1771142,"uid":40029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:58:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3ce30d5996c1a085aa3867bd161604a4c1a0d6","tid":1771142,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"大家留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b2201647ecd5876083607f52f0cb04ee8cb0e3","tid":1771142,"uid":293172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"推 大埔人唔該幫幫手"},{"pid":"2023f9738b9b4dbee79973f5e0457db63eae82e7